@startuml
[*] --> J0

state J0 <<choice>>

state "Journey Details" as JourneyDetails
JourneyDetails : entry/upon user login and destination selection
JourneyDetails : do/display journey details
JourneyDetails : exit/after viewing journey details

state "Driving Mode" as DrivingMode
DrivingMode : entry/after viewing journey details
DrivingMode : do/activate driving mode or choose other options
DrivingMode : exit/after selection

state "Place to Eat" as PlaceToEat
PlaceToEat : entry/after viewing journey details
PlaceToEat : do/select place to eat, view menu, and place order
PlaceToEat : exit/after order placed

state "Accident Notification" as AccidentNotification
AccidentNotification : entry/after viewing journey details
AccidentNotification : do/inform relevant authorities in case of an accident
AccidentNotification : exit/after notification sent

state "Driving Notifications" as DrivingNotifications
DrivingNotifications : entry/after viewing journey details
DrivingNotifications : do/send notifications during driving
DrivingNotifications : exit/after notifications sent

state "Order Confirmation" as OrderConfirmation
OrderConfirmation : entry/after viewing journey details
OrderConfirmation : do/confirm order placement
OrderConfirmation : exit/after order confirmed

J0 --> JourneyDetails [valid]
JourneyDetails --> DrivingMode [valid]
DrivingMode --> PlaceToEat [valid]
PlaceToEat --> AccidentNotification [valid]
AccidentNotification --> DrivingNotifications [valid]
DrivingNotifications --> OrderConfirmation [valid]
OrderConfirmation --> [*] [valid]
@enduml
